<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>帮助文档 - IMA Bot</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/simple-icons@v9/font/simple-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="images/lobster-icon.png">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <a href="index.html" class="logo">
                <img src="images/lobster-icon.png" alt="IMA Bot" class="logo-img">
                <span class="logo-text">IMA Bot</span>
            </a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="index.html">首页</a></li>
                <li><a href="pricing.html">定价</a></li>
                <li><a href="adopt.html">创建 Bot</a></li>
                <li><a href="docs.html" class="active">帮助</a></li>
                <li><a href="feishu-config.html">飞书配置</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.imastudio.com/" target="_blank">支持</a></li>
            </ul>
            <button class="hamburger">
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Docs Hero -->
    <section class="docs-hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>使用文档</h1>
            <p>从领养你的第一只小龙虾，到养成你的专属创作伙伴</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Docs Content -->
    <section class="docs-content">
        <div class="container">
            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div class="docs-section">
                <div class="step-header">
                    <span class="step-num">1</span>
                    <h2>领养你的小龙虾</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <h3>点击"免费领养"</h3>
                    <p>在 IMA Bot 首页点击"创建 Bot"按钮，开始创建你的专属小龙虾。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <h3>注册账号</h3>
                    <p>使用邮箱或第三方账号注册。你的 IMA Bot 账号与 IMA Studio 账号是打通的，无需重复注册。</p>
                    <div class="tip-box">
                        <span class="tip-icon">💡</span>
                        <strong>账号互通</strong>
                        <p>IMA Bot 与 IMA Studio 使用同一账号体系。你在 IMA Studio 的作品、积分、社区身份都可以在 Bot 中无缝使用。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2 -->
            <div class="docs-section">
                <div class="step-header">
                    <span class="step-num">2</span>
                    <h2>选择订阅版本</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <h3>根据需求选择套餐</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>免费版</strong>：体验 IMA 基础功能</li>
                        <li><strong>Plus 版</strong> ($9.99/月)：700 积分，适合轻度创作者</li>
                        <li><strong>Pro 版</strong> ($49.99/月)：3200 积分 + 1核2G云端，完整 Bot 功能</li>
                        <li><strong>Ultra 版</strong> ($199.99/月)：18000 积分 + 2核4G顶配，全模型全工具箱</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="pricing.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-small" style="margin-top:1rem">查看定价详情</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3 -->
            <div class="docs-section">
                <div class="step-header">
                    <span class="step-num">3</span>
                    <h2>配置你的 Bot</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <h3>选择大模型</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Kimi</strong>：长上下文，中英文均衡</li>
                        <li><strong>MiniMax</strong>：超长上下文</li>
                        <li><strong>Claude</strong>：深度推理（Ultra 专享）</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <h3>选择 Skill 工具箱</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>🎨 图片生成</strong>：文生图、图生图、编辑</li>
                        <li><strong>🎬 视频制作</strong>：字幕、转写、生成</li>
                        <li><strong>🎵 音频创作</strong>：ASR、TTS、音乐</li>
                        <li><strong>🌐 浏览器工具</strong>：网页抓取、自动操作（Ultra）</li>
                        <li><strong>🖥️ 建站工具</strong>：页面生成、部署、SEO（Ultra）</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 4 -->
            <div class="docs-section">
                <div class="step-header">
                    <span class="step-num">4</span>
                    <h2>连接聊天渠道</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <h3>将你的 Bot 连接到你常用的聊天应用，随时随地与它对话：</h3>
                    <div class="platforms-list">
                        <div class="platform-item">
                            <svg class="si" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32"><path fill="#25D366" d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.149-.149.447-.347.672-.52.174-.124.273-.198.375-.297.297-.149.446-.297.625-.446.059-.05.099-.099.149-.149.198-.198.396-.347.595-.52.348-.297.595-.52.843-.793.124-.149.223-.273.37-.347.198-.099.42-.149.645-.149.149 0 .372.05.595.149.198.149.347.347.495.52.174.198.347.42.52.694l.05.05.05.05c.272.396.546.793.818 1.164.297.397.595.793.867 1.164.124.149.223.273.347.42.198.149.42.297.665.446.149.075.27.149.37.224.124.124.174.273.273.42l.05.05a.98.98 0 0 1-.084.99c-.198.446-.446.892-.743 1.164-.372.347-.818.694-1.613 1.164-.42.248-.927.42-1.38.595-.149.05-.372.124-.53.174-.198.05-.446.124-.669.198-.198.075-.347.174-.495.297-.149.124-.223.248-.297.347l-.05.05c-.074.174-.149.372-.174.495 0 .198.05.42.124.645 0 0 .05.05.075.124.124.495.347 1.015.546 1.37.174.347.347.595.595.793.223.174.495.347.818.52.149.075.297.124.446.174.174.05.347.075.52.124.198.05.42.099.669.149.248.05.52.075.818.075.42 0 .84-.124 1.243-.372.42-.272.793-.645 1.093-1.093.347-.52.595-1.093.743-1.768.149-.744-.124-1.693-.495-2.356-.372-.673-.818-1.24-1.49-1.733-.198-.149-.372-.273-.52-.372l-.124-.074-.05-.05.05-.05.124-.124c.124-.124.248-.248.347-.372.124-.149.223-.297.297-.447.124-.198.174-.42.174-.644 0-.273-.05-.546-.149-.793 0 0-.05-.05-.074-.124-.025-.074-.074-.149-.124-.223-.05-.124-.124-.223-.198-.297-.074-.099-.173-.198-.272-.297-.124-.124-.248-.223-.42-.347l-.124-.099c-.124-.099-.223-.173-.322-.248l-.124-.074c-.099-.05-.198-.099-.297-.149l-.124-.05c-.074-.025-.149-.05-.223-.074l-.05-.025-.025-.025-.025-.025-.124-.05-.198-.074-.272-.099c-.099-.025-.198-.05-.297-.074-.124-.025-.248-.025-.372-.025-.198 0-.42.025-.644.074-.223.05-.446.149-.669.297-.223.149-.42.347-.546.595-.124.272-.174.595-.149.942.025.347.124.718.272 1.093.124.347.297.718.546 1.093.223.347.495.718.843 1.093.347.372.767.744 1.293 1.093.52.347 1.12.668 1.816.942.42.173.867.32 1.34.42.495.124 1.04.173 1.616.124.595-.05 1.24-.173 1.888-.42.347-.124.694-.297 1.04-.546.347-.248.668-.546.96-.893.075-.074.173-.173.248-.272l.05-.05c.149-.173.272-.347.347-.52.124-.223.198-.495.223-.767.025-.347-.025-.718-.149-1.093z"/></svg>
                            <div>
                                <h4>WhatsApp</h4>
                                <p>扫描二维码绑定个人 WhatsApp 账号</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="platform-item">
                            <svg class="si" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32"><path fill="#26A5E4" d="M12 0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12s5.373 12 12 12 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0zm5.562 8.248l-1.704 8.04c-.12.473-.438.827-.914.827-.264 0-.522-.096-.716-.276l-2.256-1.832-1.924 1.256c-.2.132-.464.176-.708.076l-.56-.224-2.156-1.972c-.44-.408-.444-1.08.012-1.488l8.04-4.44c.396-.22.92-.176 1.244.108z"/></svg>
                            <div>
                                <h4>Telegram</h4>
                                <p>搜索 @IMABot 或创建专属 Bot</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="platform-item">
                            <svg class="si" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32"><path fill="#4285FF" d="M21.35 3.65c-.45-.78-1.01-1.52-1.66-2.18a3.8 3.8 0 0 0-2.68-1.12c-.93 0-1.82.37-2.47 1.03A7.94 7.94 0 0 0 12.7 0c-1.2 0-2.34.33-3.35.94a4.3 4.3 0 0 0-2.98-1.3c-1.28 0-2.49.55-3.38 1.53A7.62 7.62 0 0 0 .93 5.6a9.74 9.74 0 0 0 0 4.8c.47 1.27 1.13 2.45 1.95 3.5a4.02 4.02 0 0 0 3.1 1.53c.55 1.05 1.16 2.08 1.83 3.05-.23.38-.5.76-.8 1.12a3.88 3.88 0 0 0-2.05-.45c-.62 0-1.23.12-1.8.35a4.36 4.36 0 0 0-3.1 3.2c-.14.52-.2 1.06-.18 1.6 0 1.45.73 2.78 1.97 3.6a5.68 5.68 0 0 0 3.83 1.22c1.16 0 2.27-.3 3.25-.85a4.96 4.96 0 0 0 2.55 1.32c.73 0 1.45-.18 2.08-.53a4.85 4.85 0 0 0 2.98-3.3c.27-.75.43-1.55.46-2.38.14-3.3-1.16-6.47-3.6-9.04.5-.76.9-1.58 1.17-2.45zM9.62 17.2c-1.13 0-2.04-.93-2.04-2.08s.91-2.08 2.04-2.08c1.12 0 2.03.93 2.03 2.08s-.9 2.08-2.03 2.08zm6.76 0c-1.13 0-2.04-.93-2.04-2.08s.91-2.08 2.04-2.08c1.12 0 2.03.93 2.03 2.08s-.91 2.08-2.03 2.08z"/></svg>
                            <div>
                                <h4>飞书/Lark</h4>
                                <p>企业微信授权或自建应用</p>
                                <a href="feishu-config.html" class="btn btn-small" style="margin-top:0.5rem">飞书配置指南 →</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="platform-item">
                            <svg class="si" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" height="32"><path fill="#5865F2" d="M20.317 4.37a19.791 19.791 0 0 0-4.885-1.515.074.074 0 0 0-.079.037c-.21.375-.444.864-.608 1.25a18.27 18.27 0 0 0-5.487 0 12.64 12.64 0 0 0-.617-1.25.077.077 0 0 0-.079-.037A19.736 19.736 0 0 0 3.677 4.37a.07.07 0 0 0-.032.027C.533 9.046-.32 13.58.099 18.057a.082.082 0 0 0 .031.057 19.9 19.9 0 0 0 5.993 3.03.078.078 0 0 0 .084-.028 14.09 14.09 0 0 0 1.226-1.994.076.076 0 0 0-.041-.106 13.107 13.107 0 0 1-1.872-.892.077.077 0 0 1-.008-.128 10.2 10.2 0 0 0 .372-.292.074.074 0 0 1 .077-.01c3.928 1.793 8.18 1.793 12.062 0a.074.074 0 0 1 .078.01c.12.098.246.198.373.292a.077.077 0 0 1-.006.127 12.299 12.299 0 0 1-1.873.892.077.077 0 0 0-.041.107c.36.698.772 1.362 1.225 1.993a.076.076 0 0 0 .084.028 19.839 19.839 0 0 0 6.002-3.03.077.077 0 0 0 .032-.054c.5-5.177-.838-9.674-3.549-13.66a.061.061 0 0 0-.031-.03zM8.02 15.33c-1.183 0-2.157-1.085-2.157-2.419 0-1.333.956-2.419 2.157-2.419 1.21 0 2.176 1.096 2.157 2.42 0 1.333-.956 2.418-2.157 2.418zm7.975 0c-1.183 0-2.157-1.085-2.157-2.419 0-1.333.955-2.419 2.157-2.419 1.21 0 2.176 1.096 2.157 2.42 0 1.333-.946 2.418-2.157 2.418z"/></svg>
                            <div>
                                <h4>Discord</h4>
                                <p>邀请 Bot 到服务器或 DM 对话</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tip-box">
                        <span class="tip-icon">🚀</span>
                        <strong>多平台同步</strong>
                        <p>你可以同时连接多个渠道，龙虾会在所有连接的平台同步响应。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 5 -->
            <div class="docs-section">
                <div class="step-header">
                    <span class="step-num">5</span>
                    <h2>开始对话创作</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <h3>简单任务</h3>
                    <p>对于常规创作任务，龙虾可以直接完成：</p>
                    <div class="example-box">
                        <p>"帮我生成一张赛博朋克风格的产品海报"</p>
                        <p>"把这个视频剪成 15 秒的短视频"</p>
                        <p>"写一条关于 AI 创业的小红书文案"</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 6 -->
            <div class="docs-section">
                <div class="step-header">
                    <span class="step-num">6</span>
                    <h2>训练与进化</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <h3>反馈与纠正</h3>
                    <p>当龙虾的任务完成不够好时，直接告诉它：</p>
                    <div class="example-box">
                        <p>"这个海报的颜色太暗了，换成亮一点的蓝色调"</p>
                        <p>"文案太正式了，用更口语化的风格重写"</p>
                        <p>"视频的节奏太快，前面加 2 秒缓冲"</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <h3>安装新技能</h3>
                    <p>IMA Bot 平台持续更新官方技能库。你可以随时为龙虾安装：</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>行业专属技能（电商、教育、金融等）</li>
                        <li>平台专用技能（Shopify、Notion、Figma 等）</li>
                        <li>创意技能（3D 建模、动画、音效设计）</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="tip-box">
                        <span class="tip-icon">🔄</span>
                        <strong>养成闭环</strong>
                        <p>对话创作 → 反馈训练 → 技能升级 → 龙虾进化 → 更好的创作 → 循环往复</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Final -->
            <div class="docs-section final">
                <h2>🎉 最终形态：你的超级创作大脑</h2>
                <p>经过持续训练，你的龙虾会成为：</p>
                <ul class="final-list">
                    <li><strong>懂你的风格</strong> — 知道你喜欢什么色调、什么语气、什么节奏</li>
                    <li><strong>知你的习惯</strong> — 记得你常用的平台、格式、工作流</li>
                    <li><strong>省你的时间</strong> — 复杂任务自动拆解，不需要你操心细节</li>
                    <li><strong>扩你的能力</strong> — 7×24 随时响应，同时处理多个创作项目</li>
                </ul>
                <p>就像现在与你的互动一样——你提出想法，我执行创作，你给予反馈，我持续进化。这不仅是工具，是伙伴。</p>
                <a href="adopt.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-large" style="margin-top:2rem">立即创建你的 Bot 🦞</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-brand">
                    <img src="images/lobster-icon.png" alt="IMA Bot" width="32">
                    <span>IMA Bot</span>
                    <p>基于 IMA Studio 的智能创作助手</p>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-links">
                    <a href="index.html">首页</a>
                    <a href="pricing.html">定价</a>
                    <a href="adopt.html">创建 Bot</a>
                    <a href="docs.html">帮助</a>
                    <a href="feishu-config.html">飞书配置</a>
                    <a href="https://www.imastudio.com/" target="_blank">支持</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>© 2026 IMA Studio. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
